-hike-to-the-top-of-diyaluma-falls\">2. Hike to the Top of Diyaluma Falls<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Experience nature&#x2019;s very own playground at <a href=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/sri-lanka\/diyaluma-falls-sri-lanka\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Diyaluma waterfall<\/a>! It&#x2019;s the 2nd highest waterfall in the country and one of the best places to visit in <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/sri-lanka\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Sri Lanka<\/a>. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>This incredible slice of nature is located around 40 km from <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/sri-lanka\/ella-sri-lanka\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Ella<\/a>, so it&#x2019;s a great day trip on your vacation. Ask your tuk-tuk driver to take you to the bottom of the trail. From here, you can follow the path for around 2 hours from the waterfall&#x2019;s base to the top.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Read: <\/strong><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/sri-lanka\/diyaluma-falls-sri-lanka\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Diyaluma Falls, Sri Lanka<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/20203946\/sri-lanka-best-places-3.jpg\" alt=\"sri lanka best places to visit Diyaluma Falls\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"sri lanka best places to visit Diyaluma Falls\" class=\"wp-image-71911 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/20203946\/sri-lanka-best-places-3.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/20203946\/sri-lanka-best-places-3-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/20203946\/sri-lanka-best-places-3-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/20203946\/sri-lanka-best-places-3-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/20203946\/sri-lanka-best-places-3-24x30.jpg 24w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/20203946\/sri-lanka-best-places-3-130x163.jpg 130w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/20203946\/sri-lanka-best-places-3-144x180.jpg 144w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/20203946\/sri-lanka-best-places-3-614x768.jpg 614w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/20203946\/sri-lanka-best-places-3-819x1024.jpg 819w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/20203946\/sri-lanka-best-places-3-864x1080.jpg 864w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/20203946\/sri-lanka-best-places-3-1152x1440.jpg 1152w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/20203946\/sri-lanka-best-places-3-300x375.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/20203946\/sri-lanka-best-places-3-600x750.jpg 600w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/20203946\/sri-lanka-best-places-3-24x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/20203946\/sri-lanka-best-places-3.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>Once you reach the summit, you&#x2019;ll see the three natural infinity pools perched on the edge of the cliff. Swim in the pools, chill on the rocks, and enjoy the extraordinary views, as you gaze 220 meters below. You&#x2019;ll feel as if you&#x2019;re on top of the world!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Tip:<\/strong> Please note that there are no safety barriers at the falls, so be careful when swimming close to the cliff edge.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-2 is-cropped\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/20203935\/sri-lanka-best-places-2-648x810.jpg\" alt=\"sri lanka Diyaluma Falls\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"sri lanka Diyaluma Falls\" data-id=\"71909\" data-full-url=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/20203935\/sri-lanka-best-places-2.jpg\" data-link=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/sri-lanka\/places-to-visit-sri-lanka\/attachment\/sri-lanka-best-places-2\/\" class=\"wp-image-71909 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 648px) 100vw, 648px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/20203935\/sri-lanka-best-places-2-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/20203935\/sri-lanka-best-places-2-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/20203935\/sri-lanka-best-places-2-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/20