ces-22-800x557.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/21192658\/sri-lanka-best-places-22-450x313.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/21192658\/sri-lanka-best-places-22-30x21.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/21192658\/sri-lanka-best-places-22-163x113.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/21192658\/sri-lanka-best-places-22-259x180.jpg 259w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/21192658\/sri-lanka-best-places-22-768x534.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/21192658\/sri-lanka-best-places-22-1024x713.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/21192658\/sri-lanka-best-places-22-1440x1002.jpg 1440w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/21192658\/sri-lanka-best-places-22-300x209.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/21192658\/sri-lanka-best-places-22-600x418.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/21192658\/sri-lanka-best-places-22.jpg 1920w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/21192658\/sri-lanka-best-places-22-30x21.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/21192658\/sri-lanka-best-places-22-1080x752.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>Each national park has its own unique characteristics. For example, some are known for their vast herds of elephants and others for their diversity of monkey species. Whatever you choose, there is no better experience than jumping in a jeep and riding through the long grasses and bushland of Sri Lanka. It&#x2019;s an incredible opportunity to see these majestic animals in the wild and one that you&#x2019;ll remember forever.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Read:&#xA0;<\/strong><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/sri-lanka\/national-parks-sri-lanka\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Best National Parks, Sri Lanka<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/07091455\/sri-lanka-national-parks-5.jpg\" alt=\"National Parks Sri Lanka\"><\/noscript><img width=\"261\" height=\"338\" alt=\"National Parks Sri Lanka\" class=\"wp-image-63881 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1484px) 100vw, 1484px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/07091455\/sri-lanka-national-parks-5.jpg 1484w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/07091455\/sri-lanka-national-parks-5-464x600.jpg 464w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/07091455\/sri-lanka-national-parks-5-626x810.jpg 626w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/07091455\/sri-lanka-national-parks-5-261x338.jpg 261w, https:\/\/