r trip! The stunning candy-like red and white striped mosque is named &#x2018;Jami Ul-Alfar&#x2019; and is located in the bustling Pettah district (one of the oldest parts of Colombo). The building from the outside is phenomenal, with its tall minarets towering across the city and its facade covered in red and white patterns moving in every possible direction.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>The inside is equally as beautiful, and tourists can enter and look around. However, be aware that this is a religious place of worship, and you will need to cover your hair, arms, and legs as a sign of respect.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/21193414\/sri-lanka-best-places-25.jpg\" alt=\"best places to visit sri lanka red mosque colombo\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"best places to visit sri lanka red mosque colombo\" class=\"wp-image-72013 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/21193414\/sri-lanka-best-places-25.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/21193414\/sri-lanka-best-places-25-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/21193414\/sri-lanka-best-places-25-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/21193414\/sri-lanka-best-places-25-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/21193414\/sri-lanka-best-places-25-24x30.jpg 24w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/21193414\/sri-lanka-best-places-25-130x163.jpg 130w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/21193414\/sri-lanka-best-places-25-144x180.jpg 144w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\