 perfect growing conditions. Tea production continues to live on in Sri Lanka, and the country is still one of the largest exporters of the plant today.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Read:<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/sri-lanka\/nuwara-eliya\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Explore the Lush Green Tea Plantations of Nuwara Eliya&#xA0;<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/21191636\/sri-lanka-best-places-19.jpg\" alt=\"best places to visit sri lanka tea plantations\"><\/noscript><img width=\"261\" height=\"338\" alt=\"best places to visit sri lanka tea plantations\" class=\"wp-image-71997 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1484px) 100vw, 1484px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/21191636\/sri-lanka-best-places-19.jpg 1484w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/21191636\/sri-lanka-best-places-19-464x600.jpg 464w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/21191636\/sri-lanka-best-places-19-626x810.jpg 626w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/21191636\/sri-lanka-best-places-19-261x338.jpg 261w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/21191636\/sri-lanka-best-places-19-23x30.jpg 23w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/21191636\/sri-lanka-best-places-19-126x163.jpg 126w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/21191636\/sri-lanka-best-places-19-139x180.jpg 139w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/21191636\/sri-lanka-best-places-19-594x768.jpg 594w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/21191636\/sri-lanka-best-places-19-791x1024.jpg 791w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/21191636\/sri-lanka-best-places-19-835x1080.jpg 835w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/21191636\/sri-lanka-best-places-19-1113x1440.jpg 1113w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/21191636\/sri-lanka-best-places-19-300x388.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/21191636\/sri-lanka-best-places-19-600x776.jpg 600w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/21191636\/sri-lanka-best-places-19-23x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/21191636\/sri-lanka-best-places-19.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The area is home to many factories, plantations, and tea rooms. Rent a tuk-tuk for the day and ask your driver to take you on a tour, stopping off at the many beautiful viewpoints, and drinking tea at the factories. You can also arrange for a tour of the factories to learn more about tea production and its history.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--tip \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--tip\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Tip:<\/strong> This area is also home to the incredible Ramboda waterfall, which is well worth stopping off at on your trip.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-2 is-cropped\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/21191651\/sri-lanka-best-places-20-545x810.jpg\" alt=\"sri lanka tea plantations\"><\/noscript><img width=\"227\" height=\"338\" alt=\"sri lanka tea plantations\" data-id=\"71999\" data-full-url=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/21191651\/sri-lanka-best-places-20.jpg\" data-link=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/sri-lanka\/places-to-visit-sri-lanka\/attachment\/sri-lanka-best-places-20\/\" class=\"wp-image-71999 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 545px) 100vw, 545px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/21191651\/sri-lanka-best-places-20-545x810.jpg 545w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/21191651\/sri-lanka-best-places-20-404x600.jpg 404w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/21191651\/sri-lanka-best-places-20-227x338.jpg 227w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/21191651\/sri-lanka-best-places-20-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/21191651\/sri-lanka-best-places-20-110x163.jpg 110w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/21191651\/sri-lanka-best-places-20-121x180.jpg 121w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/21191651\/sri-lanka-best-places-20-517x768.jpg 517w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/21191651\/sri-lanka-best-places-20-689x1024.jpg 689w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/21191651\/sri-lanka-best-places-20-727x1080.jpg 727w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/21191651\/sri-lanka-best-places-20-969x1440.jpg 969w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/21191651\/sri-lanka-best-places-20-300x446.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/21191651\/sri-lanka-best-places-20-600x892.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/21191651\/sri-lanka-best-places-20.jpg 1292w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/21191651\/sri-lanka-best-places-20-20x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/21191651\/sri-lanka-best-places-20-545x810.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure><\/li><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/21191702\/sri-lanka-best-places-21-545x810.jpg\" alt=\"sri lanka train tea plantations\"><\/noscript><img width=\"227\" height=\"338\" alt=\"sri lanka train tea plantations\" data-id=\"72001\" data-full-url=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/21191702\/sri-lanka-best-places-21.jp