https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/21185338\/sri-lanka-best-places-14-626x810.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure><\/li><\/ul><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>These buildings are of such cultural significance that <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/destinations\/best-unesco-world-heritage-sites\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">UNESCO<\/a> has named Galle Fort a world heritage site, promoting the continued preservation of the area. The turbulent history of invasions and colonization definitely explains the uniquely European feel in this tropical paradise!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Nowadays, visitors can enjoy visiting the ancient fort and wandering through the charming streets, full of beautiful <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/netherlands\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Dutch<\/a>-style buildings transformed into trendy shops, cafes, and restaurants.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--tip \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--tip\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Tip: <\/strong>Make sure to head down to Galle fort wall at sunset for fantastic views.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-2 is-cropped\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><div class=\"