k.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/21185753\/sri-lanka-best-places-15.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"h-8-sigiriya-lion-rock\">8. Sigiriya Lion Rock<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Sigiriya Lion Rock is known as one of the most remarkable natural phenomena globally and is one of the top places to visit in <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/sri-lanka\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Sri Lanka<\/a>! The enormous (200m) square-shaped rock emerges from the ground in the middle of a flat, dense landscape. The sheer size of the stone is totally jaw-dropping, almost looking as if it has appeared by magic. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Did you know?<\/strong> Lion Rock is one of the eight <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/travel-blog\/best-unesco-world-heritage-sites\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">UNESCO<\/a> World Heritage sights in <a href=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/sri-lanka\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Sri Lanka<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-2 is-cropped\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/21190801\/sri-lanka-best-places-18-606x810.jpg\" alt=\"sri lanka Sigiriya rock view\"><\/noscript><img width=\"253\" height=\"338\" alt=\"sri lanka Sigiriya rock view\" data-id=\"71991\" data-full-url=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/21190801\/sri-lanka-best-places-18.jpg\" data-link=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/sri-lanka\/places-to-visit-sri-lanka\/attachment\/sri-lanka-best-places-18\/\" class=\"wp-image-71991 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 606px) 100vw, 606px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/21190801\/sri-lanka-best-places-18-606x810.jpg 606w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/21190801\/sri-lanka-best-places-18-449x600.jpg 449w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/21190801\/sri-lanka-best-places-18-253x338.jpg 253w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/21190801\/sri-lanka-best-places-18-22x30.jpg 22w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/21190801\/sri-lanka-best-places-18-122x163.jpg 122w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/21190801\/sri-lanka-best-places-18-135x180.jpg 135w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/21190801\/sri-lanka-best-places-18-574x768.jpg 574w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/21190801\/sri-lanka-best-places-18-766x1024.jpg 766w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/21190801\/sri-lanka-best-places-18-808x1080.jpg 808w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/21190801\/sri-lanka-best-places-18-1077x1440.jpg 1077w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/21190801\/sri-lanka-best-places-18-300x401.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/21190801\/sri-lanka-best-places-18-600x802.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/21190801\/sri-lanka-best-places-18.jpg 1436w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/21190801\/sri-lanka-best-places-18-22x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images