places-17-614x768.jpg 614w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/21190748\/sri-lanka-best-places-17-819x1024.jpg 819w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/21190748\/sri-lanka-best-places-17-864x1080.jpg 864w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/21190748\/sri-lanka-best-places-17-1152x1440.jpg 1152w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/21190748\/sri-lanka-best-places-17-300x375.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/21190748\/sri-lanka-best-places-17-600x750.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/21190748\/sri-lanka-best-places-17.jpg 1536w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/21190748\/sri-lanka-best-places-17-24x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/21190748\/sri-lanka-best-places-17-648x810.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure><\/li><\/ul><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>Most interesting is that this rock was designed as a fortress by King Kashyapa, as far back as 477 AD! He believed this was the most strategic place because of its panoramic views of the land below. The gardens he designed on top of the rock are still there today, as well as murals and rock paintings. It will take you around 2-3 hours to explore the entire area around and on top of Sigiriya Lion Rock.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>It&#x2019;s recommended to climb Lion Rock as early as possible so that you can avoid the heat and see the epic sunrise from this elevated position.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Read:<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/sri-lanka\/sigiriya-lion-rock\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Climb the World-Famous Sigiriya Lion Rock<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/21190735\/sri-lanka-best-places-16.jpg\" alt=\"best places to visit sri lanka Sigiriya rock\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"best places to visit sri lanka Sigiriya rock\" class=\"wp-image-71986 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/21190735\/sri-lanka-best-places-16.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/21190735\/sri-lanka-best-places-16-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/21190735\/sri-lanka-best-places-16-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/21190735\/sri-lanka-best-places-16-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/21190735\/sri-lanka-best-places-16-24x30.jpg 24w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/21190735\/sri-lanka-best-places-16-130x163.jpg 130w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\