orch and climb up steep boulders before reaching the top.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Hiking up Pidurangula Rock is a magical experience that you must add to your places to visit in <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/sri-lanka\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Sri Lanka<\/a>! It also has a cheaper entrance fee than Lion Rock.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--mustread \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--mustread\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/sri-lanka\/pidurangala-rock-sigiriya\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Pidurangula Rock, Sigiriya<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/20211429\/sri-lanka-best-places-7.jpg\" alt=\"best places to visit sri lanka Pidurangula Rock\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"best places to visit sri lanka Pidurangula Rock\" class=\"wp-image-71919 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/20211429\/sri-lanka-best-places-7.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/20211429\/sri-lanka-best-places-7-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/20211429\/sri-lanka-best-places-7-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/20211429\/sri-lanka-best-places-7-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\