It&#x2019;s particularly famous for its massive collection of orchids, showcased in many varieties and colors. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Spend an afternoon here, walking among the plants, taking photos, and relaxing on the grass. There&#x2019;s also the option to sit down for a refreshing drink at one of the garden&#x2019;s cafes.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Read:<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/sri-lanka\/kandy-sri-lanka\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Kandy, Sri Lanka<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/20211731\/sri-lanka-best-places-8.jpg\" alt=\"sri lanka best places to go Kandy Botanical Gardens\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"sri lanka best places to go Kandy Botanical Gardens\" class=\"wp-image-71921 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/20211731\/sri-lanka-best-places-8.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/20211731\/sri-lanka-best-places-8-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/20211731\/sri-lanka-best-places-8-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/20211731\/sri-lanka-best-places-8-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/1